{"tid":500559,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"堅持 & 固執 , 有咩分別？","createTime":"2017-12-16T01:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T01:23:28.000Z","uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"28dc72822073d8332ebbb88189b5ea4cbf4b031e","tid":500559,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:32:18.000Z","msg":"例如我好鍾意踢波，每日都認真練習，疏於讀書<br />\n<br />\n咁我係對足球有堅持 ？ 定係固執 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5e5c1533be1ac3b58c9d0bd4a4039e025ab257","tid":500559,"uid":3454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:34:42.000Z","msg":"踢極都係渣GA 無進步 都仲要踢 咪係固執囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似袁生咁<br />\n你會話佢堅持定固執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb4e122aab98079adf1417c2928ddca22fe1ec0","tid":500559,"uid":105624,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:35:48.000Z","msg":"睇結果。最後成功左就叫堅持，都係失敗就會係固執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be543292ae2629d00c1e4eef1f7b446706e8de5","tid":500559,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踢極都係渣GA 無進步 都仲要踢 咪係固執囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似袁生咁<br />\n你會話佢堅持定固執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係有成果，就叫堅持<br />\n<br />\n冇成果，就固執 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5053d89d28954ec1b55276dcef7054befdfad226","tid":500559,"uid":50321,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:35:58.000Z","msg":"成功咗就係堅持 失敗就係固執"},{"pid":"afc28fe0eec29aa399c5d293d72af5bfaf25a67a","tid":500559,"uid":35746,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:38:57.000Z","msg":"固執係用死一個方法 諗法<br />\n<br />\n堅持係會試其他方法"},{"pid":"9d1d3cde32437d310e9dfc8557e1561a0ac9d236","tid":500559,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>固執係用死一個方法 諗法<br />\n<br />\n堅持係會試其他方法</blockquote><br />\n就以足球做例子<br />\n為堅持理想，唔讀中學，直接入足球學校全職受訓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但最後都可能冇成果 成為三四線足球員"},{"pid":"fa6feac3e5c013f1214acee6e453eb77249892fb","tid":500559,"uid":78464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:44:55.000Z","msg":"你女友堅持唔同你上床<br />\n你話佢<br />\n好固執<br />\n<br />\n堅持源於自身意志<br />\n固執源於自身/他身反省<br />\n<br />\n利申：中文F"},{"pid":"7fb49342ad153ad508bd2bd52685c1b908497803","tid":500559,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:59:57.000Z","msg":"成功叫堅持 失敗叫固執"},{"pid":"4883ce7cd4d496b70b1e3990a93b438ce798cfa0","tid":500559,"uid":129506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:21:30.000Z","msg":"你繼續踢波，但會聽其他人意見放返少少時間落讀書到，或者諗定後路，踢唔成波都有其他出路，就叫堅持<br />\n<br />\n你剩係踢波唔撚聽人意見，一意孤行就叫固執"},{"pid":"438edb9927291a083a3a07f884c4c30c17332ac6","tid":500559,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"你可能會搵到其他人同你一齊堅持<br />\n但唔可能搵到其他人同你一齊固執"},{"pid":"2b74196bc4c146d4de2f07f885bb5c858f1092da","tid":500559,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:58:19.000Z","msg":"人地鍾意你，就係堅持<br />\n<br />\n人地唔鍾意你，就係固執，死板"},{"pid":"9d3d8440ed3fa6f966dce5c641cf127b690b1115","tid":500559,"uid":60120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"堅持係比較中性，冇好冇壞<br />\n<br />\n但用得固執就係同人地講咁樣堅持係唔好<br />\n<br />\n固執比較負面<br />\n<br />\n固執多數用黎評論他人，唔會自己講自己固執<br />\n<br />\n自認固執多數係自嘲/認錯<br />\n<br />\n人地話你固執，其實就係提醒緊你咁樣堅持可能係錯"},{"pid":"d8641cad3c32566f8d1b5a392388f3ec293903e6","tid":500559,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:51:20.000Z","msg":"堅持 adverb<br />\n固執 adjective"}